== How to enter flash mode ==
Hold <code>Home</code>+<code>Volume Down</code>+<code>Power</code> then release <code>Power</code> when phone vibrates. Press <code>Volume Up</code> upon seeing warning.

== Installation ==
<code>
pmbootstrap init<br>
pmbootstrap install<br>
pmbootstrap flasher flash_kernel
</code>
* You can flash rootfs to sdcard or use netcat {{issue|456}}
* Flash rootfs to sdcard:
<code>
pmbootstrap export <br>
pmbootstrap shutdown
</code><br>
Change <code><device></code> in the following command to your sdcard!<br>
<code>sudo dd if=/tmp/postmarketOS-export/samsung-i8200.img of=/dev/<device></code>


